norswap.violin

Class Copyable.DefaultImpls

  • norswap.violin.Copyable.DefaultImpls
  • Enclosing interface:
    Copyable

    public static class Copyable.DefaultImpls

    An interface analogous to the Kotlin version of Cloneable, except that Copyable.copy is public and that Copyable.copycast is available for effortless casting.

    See Also:
    Copyable.copy, Copyable.copycast

    • Method Detail

      • copy

        public static java.lang.Object copy(Copyable $this)

        Returns a copy of the object.

        The copy is not guaranteed to be deep, meaning the copy may hold references to mutable data structures shared with the original.

      • copycast

        public static <T> T copycast(Copyable $this)

        Same as Copyable.copy, but casts the copy to T (which should be inferred, use an explicit cast otherwise).
